From: Trung Le <trung.le@ruby-journal.com>
Subject: finish FHS migration for dtinfo, backdrops, palettes, help volumes

Patch 0004 converted the hardcoded "/etc/dt" / "/usr/dt" strings inside
InfoLibSearchPath::InfoLibSearchPath to CDE_CONFIGURATION_TOP and
CDE_INSTALLATION_TOP, but Patch 0008 missed this second copy when it
split CDE_DATA_TOP out of CDE_INSTALLATION_TOP. The result on FHS
installs is that dtsearchpath probes /usr/infolib (= INSTALLATION_TOP +
"/infolib") instead of /usr/share/cde/infolib (= DATA_TOP + "/infolib"),
DTINFOLIBSEARCHPATH ends up empty, and dtinfo reports "No Infolib found
or specified" or "Infolib specification format error" depending on how
it is invoked.

The backdrops and palettes Makefiles still install under
$(CDE_DATA_TOP)/share/{backdrops,palettes} (with the legacy /share/
infix that only made sense under /usr/dt) and create a compat symlink
into $(CDE_INSTALLATION_TOP)/{backdrops,palettes}. The C side of the
desktop (compiled-in DT_BACKDROPSEARCHPATH etc.) already looks at
$(CDE_DATA_TOP)/{backdrops,palettes}, so the install layout misses
the search path. Drop the /share/ infix and the symlink hook.

Patch 0008 converted the first two help-install dirs in
doc/common/help/sdl-data.am (cmngraphdir, hfdirdir) but missed all 19
per-app graphics dirs in the same file (Appmanager, AppBuilder, ...,
Textedit), plus the sdlhelpdir line in sdl-docs.am that actually
installs the .sdl help volumes, plus the C-locale symlink hook in
doc/en_US.UTF-8/help/Makefile.am. With those still pinned to
CDE_INSTALLATION_TOP, .sdl volumes and their per-app graphics land at
/usr/dt/appconfig/help instead of /usr/share/cde/appconfig/help.
DTHELPSEARCHPATH (which dtsearchpath builds from
$(CDE_DATA_TOP)/appconfig/help) therefore probes a directory that
does not exist and ends up empty for system paths; every app's
Help > Overview pops up "The requested online help is either not
installed or not in the proper help search path." Convert the
remaining 22 occurrences.

After this:
  * /usr/share/cde/infolib/<LANG>/cde.dti/...      (was correct)
  * /usr/share/cde/backdrops/*.{pm,bm}             (was .../share/backdrops)
  * /usr/share/cde/palettes/*.dp                   (was .../share/palettes)
  * /usr/share/cde/appconfig/help/<LANG>/*.sdl     (was /usr/dt/appconfig/...)
  * dtsearchpath returns
      DTINFOLIBSEARCHPATH=/usr/share/cde/infolib/%L/%I.dti:...
      DTHELPSEARCHPATH=...:/usr/share/cde/appconfig/help/%L/%H[.sdl|.hv]
  * dtinfo finds the bundled CDE User's Guide bookcase
  * Help > Overview in every CDE app finds its volume

--- a/programs/dtsearchpath/dtsp/InfoLibSearchPath.C
+++ b/programs/dtsearchpath/dtsp/InfoLibSearchPath.C
@@ -70,8 +70,8 @@ InfoLibSearchPath::InfoLibSearchPath
     CString oldFactoryInstall = user->factoryInstall;

     // Need to re-initialize the defaults.
-    user->sysAdmConfig   = "/etc/dt";
-    user->factoryInstall = "/usr/dt";
+    user->sysAdmConfig   = CDE_CONFIGURATION_TOP;
+    user->factoryInstall = CDE_DATA_TOP;

     if (user->DTINFOLIBSP()) {
 	if (user->DTUSERINFOLIBSP()) {
